# .gitignore for TaxiPipeline project

## .NET
bin/
obj/
*.user
*.suo
*.sln.docstates
.vs/
*.vsidx

## Build results
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
[Bb]uild/
bld/

## NuGet
*.nupkg
**/[Pp]ackages/*
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets
project.lock.json

## IDE
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

## OS
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

## Data archive (keep structure, ignore archived files)
data/archive/*
!data/archive/.gitkeep

## User-specific configs (connection strings, secrets)
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.Local.json
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Local.json

## Downloaded data files
data/input/*.parquet
data/input/*.csv
data/input/*.downloading
